Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.94,0:01:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you secured the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work. I'll guide you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.05,0:01:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet up in thirty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Funell. Get this to Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cover you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now get that to Gai, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Funell...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the huge yawn for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you surfing the net or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or playing a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh. Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of them out today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you see the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently there was some terrorist attack or something yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Odaiba... no, I guess it's called "Ward 24" now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry, I'm not done with that video for the competition yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't come to harp on you about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:04:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get it done by the deadline, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now look, Shu, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go, Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he can do it, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? I think I'm trying hard to be socially perceptive here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not succeeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're way too dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm dense?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe it's true that my mind works out of step with everyone else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just that I don't know what to say to other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I hide my nervousness and go along with what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that's how I've made the quasi-friendships in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, Japan operates as a "quasi-independent" nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what my mom says.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ten years ago, the Apocalypse Virus pandemic wreaked havoc on this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and we relied on an unbelievable amount of help from many other countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And we're still dependent on them even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Japan's foundations are just barely holding together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We hear it every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"We can't leave this to you."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"You don't have the power to protect the people who are important to you."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... should we really just accept that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't there something more that I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blooming wildflower...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:07:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I beg you, please tell me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why do people fight and hurt each other?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Valiantly blooming flower...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you've got the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally didn't want to—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It... it's not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a view of my hometown, and—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, would you like a rice ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,London Bridge is falling down, falling down, falling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you're Inori, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,London Bridge is falling down, my fair lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Egoist singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}London Bridge is falling down, falling down, falling down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, more importantly, why are you so hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get this to Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu! Ouma Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might be able to do it if you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll never be able to if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouma Shu... are you a coward?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Funell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You a student?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that girl is hurt. Please don't treat her—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman is a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you defend her, we'll purge you too, as her accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does the data check show?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's definitely a member of the Funeral Parlor in Rappongi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little terrorist scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I really just accept this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I really just accept this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt... a little relieved, because I wasn't in danger anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's how pathetic I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you get right down to it, she was way out of my league.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:11:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted to get close to her, and touch her hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forget about it, Shu. Rest a while, and you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that, just go back to your normal self.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have to get this to Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? You're telling me to go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be my last chance to not hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It had to be here, of all places...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told you've dispatched a squadron to Roppongi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed it was necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll provoke unnecessary hostility.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow it if it's not for an aid mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, just how dangerous is this stolen Void Genome?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Level 3A classified information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so you can't even tell me, GHQ's Supreme Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid so, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But please, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Anti Bodies have already apprehended the culprit,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and are searching for the stolen genome as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still don't want to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been granted the authority to dispose of the diseased without warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:13:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't tell us where you hid it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to purge every single resident of this neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll regret this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention all units.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All residents in our operating area are designated as Stage IV+ infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby authorize infection control measures!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do with the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After we commence hostilities, get rid of her outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:13:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing cook rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no, I don't {\i1}think{\i0} it does...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You messin' with me? Just hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.24,0:14:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry, but it doesn't belong to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She worked so hard to protect this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings, my deceased fellows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Deceased"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The current situation doesn't allow for your survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, you are all dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got some balls, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, who is this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Funell, right? Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Ouma Shu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the girl who was with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just abandoned her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai! The GHQ whitecoats are invading!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn those bastards! They're firing live rounds at anybody they see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi, what's the word on Ayase and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy incoming on our left!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat it, you're in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare let go of that thing! Protect it this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... what can I do, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many are we up against?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure yet! More keep coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do something that's not like you for once, Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...use me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take it this time, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guilty crown given shape through the bond between hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:25.34,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}These days you love me no more
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:31.97,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}nor am I still treasured by you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:40.77,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Now I am all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:48.66,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}What did you tell me when we parted?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:55.29,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}The words hung in midair and never reached me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:22:02.05,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}I know my dreams and wishes are illusory
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:08.68,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}and yet I cannot give up on them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.72,0:22:18.69,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}You said, "Don't let go, hold onto my hand"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:25.69,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}and, "We will always be together"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:34.45,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Your hands as I held them were warm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.58,0:22:42.75,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,2000)}and tender
